One person has been injured after a small tanker, hauled by a vehicle exploded on the N1 highway near Malibongwe Drive, north of Johannesburg a short while ago. Johannesburg EMS spokesperson Xolile Khumalo says the patient has been transported to a nearby hospital for further care. Paramedics and emergency services are still on scene. EXPLOSION/ PrelimInfo Mini Trailer Tanker @itrafficgp:
